had seen something that Deep Fritz hadn't.} 44. Qe6 Qe4 $1 45. Qf6 Rg8 (45...
Qg6 $2 46. Qh4+ Kg8 47. Rxg7+ {wins.}) 46. Qg5 (46. e6 Kh8 $1) 46... Qg6 47.
Qh4+ Qh6 $11 {Once the queens come off, Black will be able to activate his
rook and bishop to reach a drawish ending:} 48. Qf6 (48. Qxh6+ Kxh6 49. Re7 Rc8
50. Re6+ Kg5 51. Rxa6 Bxe5+ 52. Kg1 Rxc3 $11) 48... Kh8 49. Qxh6+ Bxh6 50. Rf6
